				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">My beef with necro pets is the fact that mages are denied certain abilities because our pets are supposed to be superior. Abilities like root, slow, etc...  A necro can solo a mob quite effectively without a pet by rooting rotting. Mage rely on their pets more than any other class, so in my mind we deserve the strongest pets, but by a bigger margin than current PoP offers. Pre-pop, the epic stood out tall against the other pets, but those days are gone with PoP pets. Making our pets stronger as is summoned is probably not the answer, but rather give us some better items to equip on pets, like Summoned MAGICAL Plate armor. With high AC and some stats to boot.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=705852" target="_blank" class="postlink">Sage Nucci</a>
